    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "see, i thought it wasn't just me. it's like they're trying to buy my silence with a better title. like, if i'm busy managing a huge team and sitting in that office, i'm less likely to be digging into the audit trails. do you think they've assigned someone specific to watch me now that i'm in that position? maybe someone in my new direct reports who's actually reporting back to the board?",
